{"data":[{"name":"100:1","price":"鼻息を荒げて疾駆するもの¹にかけて、²","arabic":"وَٱلۡعَٰدِيَٰتِ ضَبۡحٗا","category":["100 (Al-Aadiyat)","Al-Aadiyat","Surah Al-Aadiyat"],"ayahNumber":6147,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　大方の解釈学者は、アーヤ*５まで登場する、この「疾駆」し「火花を散らし」「進撃する」ものを、アッラー*の道において敵を目指して駆ける馬と解釈している。「ハッジ*におけるラクダ」という説もあるが、その場合、アーヤ*５までの解釈は、本文訳とは多少変わって来る（アル＝クルトゥビー２０：１６０参照）。 ２　アーヤ*１－３までの、アッラー*によるこの誓いについては、整列者章１の訳注を参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wal-ʿādiyāti ḍabḥan ","translations":["By the racers","panting","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["wal-ʿādiyāti","ḍabḥan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1840],[2,1840,2865]]}},{"name":"100:2","price":"また、（蹄で石を）打ち付けつつ、火花を散らすものにかけて、","arabic":"فَٱلۡمُورِيَٰتِ قَدۡحٗا","category":["100 (Al-Aadiyat)","Al-Aadiyat","Surah Al-Aadiyat"],"ayahNumber":6148,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"fal-mūriyāti qadḥan ","translations":["And the producers of sparks","striking","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["fal-mūriyāti","qadḥan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1810],[2,1810,2785]]}},{"name":"100:3","price":"また、朝に（敵陣へと）進撃するものにかけて（誓う）、","arabic":"فَٱلۡمُغِيرَٰتِ صُبۡحٗا","category":["100 (Al-Aadiyat)","Al-Aadiyat","Surah Al-Aadiyat"],"ayahNumber":6149,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"fal-mughīrāti ṣub'ḥan ","translations":["And the chargers","(at) dawn","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["fal-mughīrāti","ṣub'ḥan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1680],[2,1680,2715]]}},{"name":"100:4","price":"それらは、それ¹によって埃を巻き上げ、","arabic":"فَأَثَرۡنَ بِهِۦ نَقۡعٗا","category":["100 (Al-Aadiyat)","Al-Aadiyat","Surah Al-Aadiyat"],"ayahNumber":6150,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　この「それ」とは、疾駆と、敵への進撃のこと（アッ＝サアディー９３２頁参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"fa-atharna bihi naqʿan ","translations":["Then raise","thereby","dust","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["fa-atharna","bihi","naqʿan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1000],[2,1000,1760],[3,1760,2695]]}},{"name":"100:5","price":"それ¹と共に、（敵の）集団の只中へと進み込む²、","arabic":"فَوَسَطۡنَ بِهِۦ جَمۡعًا","category":["100 (Al-Aadiyat)","Al-Aadiyat","Surah Al-Aadiyat"],"ayahNumber":6151,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　この「それ」には、「朝の時間」「疾駆」「埃」といった解釈がある（アル＝バイダーウィー５：５２０参照）。 ２　あるいは「（敵の）只中に、集団で入り込む」という意味（イブン・カスィール８：４６６参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"fawasaṭna bihi jamʿan ","translations":["Then penetrate (in the) center","thereby","collectively","(5)"],"transliterationArr":["fawasaṭna","bihi","jamʿan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1060],[2,1060,1740],[3,1740,3245]]}},{"name":"100:6","price":"本当に人間は、自分の主*に対してまさしく恩知らずであり、","arabic":"إِنَّ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنَ لِرَبِّهِۦ لَكَنُودٞ","category":["100 (Al-Aadiyat)","Al-Aadiyat","Surah Al-Aadiyat"],"ayahNumber":6152,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"inna al-insāna lirabbihi lakanūdun ","translations":["Indeed","mankind","to his Lord","(is) surely ungrateful","(6)"],"transliterationArr":["inna","al-insāna","lirabbihi","lakanūdun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1170],[2,1170,3420],[3,3420,4730],[4,4730,7605]]}},{"name":"100:7","price":"本当にかれ¹は、そのことにおける確かな証言者である。","arabic":"وَإِنَّهُۥ عَلَىٰ ذَٰلِكَ لَشَهِيدٞ","category":["100 (Al-Aadiyat)","Al-Aadiyat","Surah Al-Aadiyat"],"ayahNumber":6153,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　この「かれ」が誰かについては、「人間」「アッラー*」という説がある（アル＝クルトゥビー２０：１６２参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-innahu ʿalā dhālika lashahīdun ","translations":["And indeed, he","on","that","surely (is) a witness","(7)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-innahu","ʿalā","dhālika","lashahīdun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1950],[2,1950,2630],[3,2630,3560],[4,3560,6685]]}},{"name":"100:8","price":"また、本当に彼（人間）は、善きもの¹への愛情において、ことさら激しい者である。","arabic":"وَإِنَّهُۥ لِحُبِّ ٱلۡخَيۡرِ لَشَدِيدٌ","category":["100 (Al-Aadiyat)","Al-Aadiyat","Surah Al-Aadiyat"],"ayahNumber":6154,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　この「善きもの」は、財産のこと（ムヤッサル６００頁参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-innahu liḥubbi al-khayri lashadīdun ","translations":["And indeed he","in (the) love","(of) wealth","(is) surely intense","(8)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-innahu","liḥubbi","al-khayri","lashadīdun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2090],[2,2090,2930],[3,2930,3840],[4,3840,7055]]}},{"name":"100:9","price":"一体、彼は（何が自分を待ち受けているか、）知らないのか？墓の中にあるもの（死んだ人々）が、ひっくり返され（て、清算と報いのために蘇らされ）、","arabic":"۞ أَفَلَا يَعۡلَمُ إِذَا بُعۡثِرَ مَا فِي ٱلۡقُبُورِ","category":["100 (Al-Aadiyat)","Al-Aadiyat","Surah Al-Aadiyat"],"ayahNumber":6155,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"afalā yaʿlamu idhā buʿ'thira mā fī al-qubūri ","translations":["But does not","he know","when","will be scattered","what","(is) in","the graves","(9)"],"transliterationArr":["afalā","yaʿlamu","idhā","buʿ'thira","mā","fī","al-qubūri",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,910],[2,910,1750],[3,1750,2470],[4,2470,3400],[5,3400,3750],[6,3750,3980],[7,3980,7065]]}},{"name":"100:10","price":"胸の内にある（善悪の）ことが明らかにされる時、","arabic":"وَحُصِّلَ مَا فِي ٱلصُّدُورِ","category":["100 (Al-Aadiyat)","Al-Aadiyat","Surah Al-Aadiyat"],"ayahNumber":6156,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"waḥuṣṣila mā fī al-ṣudūri ","translations":["And is made apparent","what","(is) in","the breasts","(10)"],"transliterationArr":["waḥuṣṣila","mā","fī","al-ṣudūri",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1120],[2,1120,1530],[3,1530,1730],[4,1730,4815]]}},{"name":"100:11","price":"本当に彼らの主*は（復活の）その日、彼ら（の行い）をまさしく通暁されるお方であられる。¹","arabic":"إِنَّ رَبَّهُم بِهِمۡ يَوۡمَئِذٖ لَّخَبِيرُۢ","category":["100 (Al-Aadiyat)","Al-Aadiyat","Surah Al-Aadiyat"],"ayahNumber":6157,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　アッラー*は復活の日*以外でも、全てを通暁されるお方である。ここで「その日」と限定されているのは、報いの日*に対する警告の意味（イブン・ジュザイ２：６０２参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"inna rabbahum bihim yawma-idhin lakhabīrun ","translations":["Indeed","their Lord","about them","that Day","(is) surely All-Aware","(11)"],"transliterationArr":["inna","rabbahum","bihim","yawma-idhin","lakhabīrun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1310],[2,1310,3300],[3,3300,3900],[4,3900,5100],[5,5100,8715]]}}],"chapter":["100 (Al-Aadiyat)","Al-Aadiyat","Surah Al-Aadiyat","Chapter Al-Aadiyat","Aadiyat","Surah Aadiyat","Chapter Aadiyat","Al Aadiyat","Surah Al Aadiyat","Chapter Al Aadiyat","Surah 100","Chapter 100","The Chargers","العاديات"],"version":{"key":"japanese_saeedsato","direction":"ltr","language_iso_code":"ja","version":"1.0.10","last_update":1709035504,"title":"Japanese translation - Saeed Sato","description":"Translation of the Quran meanings into Japanese by Saeed Sato. printed in 1440 H."}}